title: Revenue of the Minnesota Vikings ( NFL ) 2001 to 2018
summary: Overall Revenue in million U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is roughly increasing from 2007 to 2008, roughly constant from 2008 to 2012, gradually increasing from 2012 to 2016, and lastly roughly constant from 2016 to 2017.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Revenue in million U.S. dollars, about 408.0 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 195.0 was reported at Year 2007
